":"very"},{"pos":"adv","gloss":"extremely"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Adverbial accusative of جِدّ (jidd, “seriousness”)."},"ipa":["/d͡ʒid.dan/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n5268","headword_ar":"جَدًا","root":"jdw","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadowaY","text_ar":"جَدْوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. ―         -b2-  Hence, (Har p. 32,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadFA","text_ar":"جَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) also written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadFY","text_ar":"جَدًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISk, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTarN jadFA","text_ar":"مَطَرٌ جَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and, accord. to the K, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadowaY","text_ar":"جَدْوَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this latter is not known except as signifying “ a gift, ” (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A common,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"general, rain;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of wide extent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which the uttermost is not known."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) One says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samaA='N jadFA","text_ar":"سَمَا=ءٌ جَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rain having a rain following it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"making the latter word masc. because it has the force of an inf. n. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aal~`hum~a A@soqinaA gadaqFA wajadFA TabaqFA","text_ar":"اَلّٰهُمَّ ا@سْقِنَا غَدَقًا وَجَدًا طَبَقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O God, water us with a copious rain, and a rain that shall cover the land"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, TA:) occurring in a trad. respecting prayer for rain. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayorN jadFA","text_ar":"خَيْرٌ جَدًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ample good;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of wide extent to men."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A=tiyka jadaA Ald~ahori","text_ar":"لَا ا=تِيكَ جَدَا الدَّهْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * K, * TA) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will not come to thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ever,"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yada Ald~ahori","text_ar":"يَدَ الدَّهْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the end of time."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","ISk","TA","S"]}]}}